Erstellen eines Vektor Tile Sets mit Tippecanoe
tippecanoe --coalesce-densest-as-needed --output-to-directory directory output_nodes.create_geojson
oder
tippecanoe --no-feature-limit --no-tile-size-limit --no-tile-compression --output-to-directory directory output_nodes.create_geojson

Erstellen von mbtiles mit Tippecanoe
# tippecanoe --no-feature-limit --no-tile-size-limit --no-tile-compression --output your_output_file.mbtiles input.create_geojson

Tippecanoe Github
https://github.com/mapbox/tippecanoe